description: Dental care or dentalcare is the maintenance of healthy teeth and may refer to: Oral hygiene, the professional care of teeth, including professional oral hygiene and dental surgery.

Normally the body's natural defenses and good oral health care, such as daily brushing and flossing, keep bacteria under control. However, without proper oral hygiene, such as tooth decay and gum disease.
